						               													<description>Full Throttle! is an expansion kit for any of the three &amp;quot;Legend&amp;quot; games covering the Mille Miglia road races across Italy &amp;ndash; Legend: The History of 1000 Miglia, Legend: Winds of War, and Legend: The 1000 Miglia Action Game. Full Throttle! adds more player interaction, competition and fun to all three games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Full Throttle! includes two decks of cards: the 72 full-sized card Main deck (used in game play) and the 40 mini card Locales deck (used as reminder markers).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are 12 different card types in the Main deck, consisting of 7 obstacles which can negatively affect a player, and 5 situations that can negatively or positively affect the chance of the obstacle's effect. The obstacles are: Pothole, Landslide, Spectators, Animal, Intersection, Fog, and Railroad Crossing Gate Down. The situations are Fatigue, Hangover, Sober Up, Fog Lifts, and Railroad Crossing Gate Up.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Main deck cards are organized into 6 suits: Mountains, Forest, Farmlands, Towns, Bad Roads, and Night. The Locales deck consists of 6 card types corresponding to the suits in the Main deck.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
